WEBVTT

00:00:00.698 --> 00:00:04.302
About 200 years ago,

00:00:04.326 --> 00:00:07.917
Napoleon famously warned ...

00:00:09.595 --> 00:00:13.934
He said, "Let China sleep,

00:00:13.958 --> 00:00:16.018
for when she wakes,

00:00:16.042 --> 00:00:17.792
she will shake the world."

00:00:19.208 --> 00:00:21.976
Despite this early warning,

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.101
the West chose to go to sleep

00:00:25.125 --> 00:00:29.851
at precisely the moment
when China and India

00:00:29.875 --> 00:00:32.333
and the rest of Asia woke up.